query:
SELECT first.id as first, last.id as last
                FROM
                    (
                        SELECT order_key as id
                        FROM ceramic_one_event
                        WHERE
                            order_key > $1 AND order_key < $2
                        ORDER BY order_key ASC
                        LIMIT 1
                    ) as first
                JOIN
                    (
                        SELECT order_key as id
                        FROM ceramic_one_event
                        WHERE
                            order_key > $1 AND order_key < $2
                        ORDER BY order_key DESC
                        LIMIT 1
                    ) as last;
